snippet.title: Bradley Cooper Reveals He Was Held At Knifepoint On NYC Subway: 'My Guard Was Down'
snippet.description: Bradley Cooper is opening up about a scary encounter. The 46-year-old actor was on Monday's episode of Dax Sherpard's "Armchair Expert" podcast and revealed that someone pulled a knife on him while he was on the subway in New York City. The incident happened in October 2019 while he was wearing noise-canceling headphones on his way to pick up his then 2-year-old daughter Lea from school. "I look down and I see a knife," he said.
